  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 8-10 min or until fork-tender, then drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, pat your <strong>basa fillets</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to a bowl with your<strong> BBQ sauce </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together so the basa fillets are fully coated in BBQ sauce, then set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>apple[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>apple disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>apple matchsticks </strong>and <strong>grated carrot</strong> in a  bowl with your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red cabbage & apple slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated basa fillets</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until charred on the outside and cooked through – this is your <strong>BBQ basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped dill</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onions</strong> to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby potato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/bbq-basa-with-herby-potato-salad-and-red-cabbage-and-apple-slaw/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>BBQ basa</strong> with the <strong>herby potato salad</strong> and <strong>red cabbage & apple slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
